n cư bách vịnh kỳ 051 - 山居百詠其五十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-4ILmxZ7vXHQA8RzMNAOyRA">Thuật hoài kỳ 2 - 述懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%C3%B4ng/Th%C6%B0-b%C3%BAt-ng%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%A9/poem-wCZSidCOKwxQUpvu1aznJA">Thư bút ngự tứ - 書筆御賜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%C3%B4ng/author-PRRViDEUcofbPpl8eY2_qg">Lê Hiển Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/V%C4%83n-h%E1%BB%AFu-%C4%91%C4%83ng-ti%E1%BB%83u-khoa-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%C3%BD/poem-vhs8tJlNKVOgxWpFqZUYpw">Văn hữu đăng tiểu khoa đề ký - 聞友登小科題寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-tVCgetl94ylIpxXT-wJP2g">Phan Quế</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
